The paper also introduces a novel dynamic programming algorithm, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed approach in the context of action classification and object detection, which are both topics related to computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
